  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "dental receptionist/assistant",
  "description": "<p>We're seeking experienced/new Dental Receptionist/Assistant to join our growing team at We Care Dental Surgery in the Bukit Merah Central Region.<br /></p><p>$2000-$3200 depending on experience.<br /></p><p><strong>What you'll be doing</strong></p><ul><li>Greeting and welcoming patients warmly, ensuring a positive patient experience</li><li>Handling patient enquiries, scheduling appointments, and managing the front desk efficiently</li><li>Assisting dentists during examinations and procedures by preparing equipment and materials</li><li>Sterilising and maintaining dental instruments and equipment</li><li>Ensuring the dental surgery and waiting area are clean, tidy and well-stocked</li><li>Providing general administrative support as needed</li></ul><p><strong>What we're looking for</strong></p><ul><li>Strong communication and interpersonal skills to engage with patients of all ages</li><li>Excellent organisational and multitasking abilities to manage a busy front desk</li><li>Attention to detail and a commitment to maintaining high standards of cleanliness and infection control</li><li>Proficiency in using dental practice management software and other relevant technology</li><li>A friendly, professional and empathetic demeanour to provide top-notch patient care</li></ul><p><strong>What we offer</strong></p><ul><li>Competitive salary and performance-based bonuses</li><li>Supportive and collaborative work environment</li><li>Discounted dental treatments for employees and their families</li><li>No experience needed, training will be provided</li></ul><p><strong>Apply now</strong> to join our growing team and be a part of our mission to deliver exceptional dental care.</p><p>Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted</p><p>Email at wecaredentalsg@gmail.com or WhatsApp 88828660.</p>",
